<text>Lipid metabolism; sphingolipid metabolism.</text>
</comment>
<comment type="subunit">
<text evidence="4">Heterodimer with SPTLC1. Component of the serine palmitoyltransferase (SPT) complex, composed of LCB1/SPTLC1, LCB2 (SPTLC2 or SPTLC3) and ssPT (SPTSSA and SPTSSB).</text>
</comment>
